Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.76,0:25:45.62,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}务必觅得
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.70,0:25:50.90,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}微眠之约
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.26,0:26:11.75,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}萌生此等惬意  实乃徒增彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.08,0:26:22.72,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}予君之意  君不知乎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.45,0:26:28.59,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}察其目光  未萦他意
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.91,0:26:33.88,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}宛如待友  毫无二致
